mp2fn - Mario's Picross to FreeNono Converter
----------------------------------------------
author:  Christian Wichmann
date:    2010-12-19
version: 0.1


DESCRIPTION
-----------
mp2fn is a converter to extract the information from Nintendo GameBoy(tm) screenshots. It reads the image files and copies the nonogram data into the FreeNono file format.


LICENSE
-------
mp2fn is released under the GNU General Public License v2 or newer.


REQUIREMENTS
------------
PIL Python Imaging Library (http://www.pythonware.com/products/pil/)


PROBLEMS
--------
Please go to http://www.freenono.org/ to submit bug reports,
request new features, etc.


